snippet.title: Wild Dose - Back to the real world...
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1379270/Wild_Dose_First_Session/
In this game, earth has become a giant city and augmentations are the new standard. To escape from this urban hell, legal drugs are delivered directly from networks to neural implants. Hackers also deal illegal versions of these drugs. The deadliest one is called Wild Dose.
